('04e3b0dbffe4dd56249e50528767f01e','febb87ca2013ee0561c4be5ef9e538a0','en','Billiards Masters Shouldn\'t Miss It-Smashing Star',NULL,'avalonweb','<div class=\"lake-content\">\n<p id=\"uc2b5afcb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">If you like playing billiards, you shouldn\'t miss Smashing Star. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">This is a game that combines catapult and PVP confrontation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">In the arena, both side can have 4 characters, and each character will catapult alternately according to the speed, and the angle of the catapult is one of the key factors to win.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652171099207微信截图_20220510161626.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"254\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u43bb43b6\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Players need to make the best catapult plan according to the attributes and skill of each character and their position on the battlefield, so that make your characters hit others as more as possible. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Moving tracks with colors will be left in the arena, and the player who occupies 66% of graffiti area first will win.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"ua1ff71a1\" class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652171077190微信截图_20220509190234_副本.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"678\" height=\"600\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u9c8b91d3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">If you are a billiard fan, then you must can make a prediction that what angle to catapult from will occupy more graffiti area. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">On the one hand, you need to find the areas that haven\'t been occupied or have been occupied by others. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">On the other hand, you need to cause more damage by hitting opponents and get more catapult chances.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/165217104727610.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"529\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"udfb3eedb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">It is very important to cause damage to opponent, because when opponent\'s characters die, you will have more catapult oppotunities during the cooldown time. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">In short, this is a game where you need to maximize your profit by finding the right catapult angle. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">If you like to play billiards, this game will be perfect for you.</span></p>\n</div>','zhourongling',1,'http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521677119805.jpg','2022-04-26 17:42:24','2022-05-10 17:24:47'),
('0965f6aa27d22856c351214b7b9edd81','febb87ca2013ee0561c4be5ef9e538a0','en','Smashing Star！Paint The Universe With Your COLOR!',NULL,'avalonweb','<div class=\"lake-content\">\n<p id=\"u2f9164c9\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Attention!</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Smashing Star is a decompressing and super attractive PVP game.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">In the arena, we combine catapult and graffiti together instead of the traditional confrontation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">The battle victory is determined by the area size of graffiti left by fights.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652162630946微信截图_20220509190117_副本.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"679\" height=\"600\" /></p>\n<p id=\"u36294f50\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u163e3011\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">In the arena, you and your opponent each have four characters with different attributes and skills to fight.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> After you decide the strategies and catapult the characters out, thier moving tracks will be left on the battlefield in the form of graffiti.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">The player who first reaches 66% of graffiti area wins the battle!</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&nbsp;<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652162804327微信截图_20220509190234_副本.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"678\" height=\"600\" /></span></p>\n<p id=\"u074cd59b\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"ua0cbecc0\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Of course it\'s not just a catapult skill game.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">You will be able to collect a variety of characters in the game as well, but only 4 of them can be selected to fight each time.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> Each hit will cause a damage to the opponent\'s characters until they die, and they will not back to the arena until the cooldown time is over.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> Therefore, keeping the characters alive as long as possible will get more chances and possibility to win.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/165216323593404_副本.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"412\" /></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u35d210f4\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<p id=\"u4b2808c6\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">In《Smashing Star》, the stronger your characters are, you will be more likely to win.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> So how to obtain more stronge characters?</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Winning arena battle can obtain new characters and new treasure chests.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">There are a lot of character cards in the treasure chests that can upgrade level and attributes of your characters, which helps you to match up a better deck!</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521634513253.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"530\" /></span></p>\n<p id=\"ua21b7913\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"uec9c0845\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<p id=\"u54c7dc7b\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Come to《Smashing Star》and be a \"Physics + Art\" player!</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">If you want to learn more about the game and relevent events.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Click </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\"><a style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5\">https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">to join our Discord Server.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Looking forward to your participation!</span></span></p>\n</div>','zhourongling',1,'http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521635188501.jpg','2022-04-26 21:33:13','2022-05-10 17:25:01'),
('4732d6ccb2897782d3644bbfd65612d8','febb87ca2013ee0561c4be5ef9e538a0','en','Configure Your Deck, Show Your Skills In Smashing Star',NULL,'avalonweb','<div class=\"lake-content\">\n<p id=\"ucf5b208b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">In Smashing Star arena, you need to maintain vigilance all the time due to ever-changing situation, also your catapult skill and fight strategy will affect the whole battle. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">From the deck design to random buff competing in battle, your each move will affect the outcome. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Properly configuring your battle deck is the first skill you need to master!</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u6fc07473\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652163784479未标题-1_副本.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"285\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u57818b0b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Each </span><span class=\"ne-text\">character</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> has five different attributes, including attack, HP, speed, respawn speed and size. The skills will be unlocked as the </span><span class=\"ne-text\">characters </span><span class=\"ne-text\">upgrade.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521642123845.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"532\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"ua3718e0b\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p id=\"ucf4898cb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">In the battle, the order of attacking is determined by speed. </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">You can choose one </span><span class=\"ne-text\">character </span><span class=\"ne-text\">to hit, attack value determines the damage;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">HP value determines the damage it can sustain;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">When characters die, there will be a cooldown time, the faster respawn speed is, the shorter cooldown time is.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521648946628.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"529\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u8c1f75d6\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p id=\"u5547b127\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Size is a special attribute, it determines the sustaining times and force of each catapult. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">The bigger size the character is, the longer track will be made and the larger graffiti area will be occupied. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">But accordingly, their speed will be slower.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u447c6d5b\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p id=\"u770c4e9a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">To sum up, you need to configure your deck according to your strategy.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/165216527300210.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"529\" /></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">If you focus on speed and want more frequent catapults, you can choose the characters with faster speed; </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">If you focus on attacking and want to take advantage of opponent\'s death, then you can choose the characters with stronger power. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Of course, there is no absolutely superior deck in Smashing Star, you need to consider your strategy and try to find your best deck!</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652165193476微信截图_20220510144340.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"421\" /></p>\n<p id=\"ufec75298\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p id=\"ub26ce520\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">If you want to learn more about the game and relevent events, please click <span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\"><a style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5\">https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5</a></span></span><span class=\"ne-text\">&nbsp;to join our official Discord Server!</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\"> Looking forward to your participation!</span></span></p>\n</div>','zhourongling',1,'http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521683806827.jpg','2022-04-26 21:32:58','2022-05-10 17:24:58'),
