('7438de4c19fcc970e635de1b30c2f69f','febb87ca2013ee0561c4be5ef9e538a0','en','My Boss Is A Cat, My Colleague Is A Cat Too!',NULL,'avalonweb','<div class=\"lake-content\">\n<p id=\"ud30de74c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Hello everyone, I am an employee of a game company and what I want to tell you is that my boss is a cat and my colleague is also a cat! </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">We finished this game called Smashing Star together.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652169241397英文.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"292\" /></span></p>\n<p id=\"u7d4b85ce\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p id=\"ue4d07fde\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Every day when I come to work, my cat boss would patrol around and supervise us to start the new day, it is said that he has a very rich game development experience and is also a veteran player.</span></p>\n<p id=\"ud27c9b18\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652170192885微信截图_20220510155813.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"472\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"ud589ac9c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Next is my cat colleague, this cat is indeed a veteran since he has been working in the company for many years, as long as the boss comes, he will work seriously, but as long as the boss walks away, he will be lying on his workstation and sleeping!</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"ud5b7b637\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652169307604微信图片_20220510155441.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"358\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u4ba7314b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">We worked together (two cats and a bunch of people) and completed&nbsp; Smashing Star, it is a competitive game where players need to control characters and leave graffiti on the arena by catapulting, and the final winner is determined by the size of the graffiti.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"uc43e4faa\" class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&nbsp;if you are interested in it, you can come to our Discord Group to communicate with us (<span style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\"><a style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5\">https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5</a></span></span><a class=\"ne-link\" style=\"color: #7e8c8d;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/Zsw7AM8pCp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-href=\"https://discord.gg/Zsw7AM8pCp\"><span class=\"ne-text\">),</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\"> my cat boss and cat colleague will also be there.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"uc0a6d0c7\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Thanks to my cat boss and cat colleague, the whole development process was full of joy. The cat boss\' patrol made me diligent, the cat colleagues\' sleep made me work harder, and finally we finished such a game.</span></p>\n</div>','zhourongling',1,'http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521686721088.jpg','2022-04-26 17:28:07','2022-05-10 16:21:48'),
('76eb17f856052c92b48b53ea01da56b5','febb87ca2013ee0561c4be5ef9e538a0','en','Create Your Graffiti Anytime, Anywhere!',NULL,'avalonweb','<div class=\"lake-content\">\n<p id=\"u535542f3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Graffiti sounds like a very street art creation, and its joy belongs to a small group of people. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">But in Smashing Star, all players can enjoy the joy and art creation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652171224061B-大图_看图王.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"292\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"ud6d3351b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Smashing Star is a PVP game that combines catapult and graffiti, both sides can have 4 characters in the arena, and each character will catapult alternately according to the speed. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Each catapult will leave tracks, after the battle, graffiti artwork is born.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652171262971微信截图_20220509190117_副本.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"530\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"ua2e7cfcf\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Here, two identical artwork would never appear. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">You and your opponent aren\'t just playing against each other, you\'re also creating art together, and the arena is your drawing board.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> If your opponent is as interesting as you are, you can even work together to create special shapes.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u0a3cfbf6\" class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">No need to go to the street or buy paints, come to Smashing Star and you can create your art anytime and anywhere. </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">If you want to share your graffiti with us, please join our Discord Server <span style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\"><a style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5\">https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5</a></span></span></span></p>\n</div>','zhourongling',1,'http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521711902672.jpg','2022-04-26 17:28:39','2022-05-10 16:29:10'),
('d906f5158cd3c60b64b73a9015a843d0','febb87ca2013ee0561c4be5ef9e538a0','en',' Smash And Doodle To Win, Show Your Skills In Smashing Star','','avalonweb','<div class=\"lake-content\">\n<p id=\"u53cc57f1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">This is a game that combines \"Physics and Art\".</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">In Smashing Star, </span><span class=\"ne-text\">you can try to complete different paintings by catapulting graffiti against your opponent.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\"> To win, you need not only a strong deck, but also excellent catapult skills.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/165217142486413.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"531\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u8d97bb0f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">I believe we have all played a lot of catapult games, the common point of these games is to get maximum benefit by precise angle and strength.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> In Smashing Star you need to find your strategies according to the current situation. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">For example, you can choose to hit those characters with lower HP first to make them loss power; </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Or you can also choose to hit those characters with bigger size, which can leave longer tracks to help you approaching 66% of graffiti area faster.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652172121958111.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"529\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u1d4685c6\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">The position of the characters is very important. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">How to occupy more graffiti area through a single catapult, while as far as possible to prevent the opponent having more chances, both need practical experience.</span></p>\n<p id=\"u00650a4c\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521723353621222.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"531\" /></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u4ea7905e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Besides hitting opponent\'s characters, there will be a buff in the middle of the arena every once in a while, some of them can improve the character\'s speed, some can add HP.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> No matter what buff it is will effect the battle. During the buff period, you must occupy buff area first, which means you need to paint graffiti where the buff is located.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521735301183333.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"529\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"u847579c7\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">A good catapult can even allow you to turn defeat into victory, to win with weakness and completely turn the situation around. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Anyways, the graffiti area will </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">determine the win and lose, the player who first reaches the 66% of graffiti area will win the battle. </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Each battle will become extremely splendid!</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"uab5fe6e7\" class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\"> If you want to learn more about the game and relevent events, please click <span style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\"><a style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5\">https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5</a></span></span><span class=\"ne-text\">&nbsp;to join our official Discord Server! </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Looking forward to your participation!</span></span></p>\n</div>','zhourongling',1,'http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521660152243.jpg','2022-04-26 17:42:50','2022-05-10 17:24:54'),
('efd9199e9d99380025c3220cb97122e3','febb87ca2013ee0561c4be5ef9e538a0','en','Join Our Discord Server, Receiving More Game Consult And Events!',NULL,'avalonweb','<div class=\"lake-content\">\n<p id=\"ubc02f3bf\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">If you are interested in Smashing Star, please join our official Discord server and freely communicate with us.&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">In the Discord group, you can participate various events to get rewards, and also can communicate with our development team, aquiring first-hand information.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/1652166734329微信截图_20220510150841.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"386\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">About this server, it is the place where we want to communicate with our players. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">Here we will post information about our games, as well as collect your suggestions and questions.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"> Therefore, we have divided different channels for different contents.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&mdash;WELCOME&mdash;</span></strong></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#welcome Channel for sending welcome messages to new members.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#rules For a good communication environment and server security, please make sure to check these rules.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#react-roles Sometimes there are events for a particular game, and it\'s easier to participate if you have the corresponding roles.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&mdash;AVALON NEWS&mdash;</span></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#current-events Some event announcements will be posted here. For example, the latest game testing plans, or some special game events.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#game-update As its name says, new content update in game will be posted here.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#preview-spotlight Sometimes we also post content that is in development, in the form of pictures or videos.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&mdash;ASK THE AVALON TEAM&mdash;</span></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#how-to-ask-questions Help us understand the questions you want to know.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#avalon-team-answers Developer responses will be posted here.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#submit-your-question A channel dedicated to submitting questions, please do not make off-topic talk in this channel.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&mdash;AVALONGAMER\'S GUILD&mdash;</span></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#we-want-you When the members of a game reaches a certain number, we will recruit moderators and open a separate server for it.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#videos-and-streams The official video or live link will be shared here.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&mdash;COMMUNITY CONTENT&mdash;</span></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#off-topic Stay polite and talk about anything you want!</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#cute-animals Share cute animals\' pictures.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#show-time Share your wonderful moments in the game.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">&mdash;GAME IN TEST STAGE&mdash;</span></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#test-announcement Announcements related to game testing.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#test-game-chat Talk about everything in the test game here.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#test-bug-report It would be better if you could provide screenshots or videos when you report bugs.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\">#test-suggestions Any suggestions are appreciated! What you are satisfied with or what you are not satisfied with.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p id=\"uf090d146\" class=\"ne-p\"></p>\n<p id=\"ub0fbbd5f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">If you want to learn more about the game and relevent events, please click <span style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\"><a style=\"color: #f1c40f; background-color: #34495e;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5\">https://discord.gg/NWqHD4zUe5</a></span></span><span class=\"ne-text\">&nbsp;to join our official Discord Group! </span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"ne-p\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #7e8c8d;\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Looking forward to your participation!</span></span></p>\n</div>','zhourongling',1,'http://corp-all-web-rs-test.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/gameWeb/Catapult/16521662413974.jpg','2022-04-26 17:42:37','2022-05-10 17:24:51');

